data.description: Newly constructed in 2022, this contemporary townhome in the gated community of Cristal Cay, Cutler Bay, offers modern living at its finest. With a 1-car garage, the first floor features stylish tile flooring, while the second floor is adorned with carpeting. The kitchen boasts stainless steel appliances and granite countertops, overlooking the dining and family areas. All bedrooms are situated upstairs, with the master bedroom featuring a walk-in closet and ensuite bathroom with dual sinks and a walk-in shower. Community amenities include Pool, clubhouse, gym, dog park, and lake walkways
